reviews.text:
I’m sorry to disappoint anyone who is planning to come for dinner. One strong reason is professionalism which it is still lacking. 

Atmosphere: loud 
Hygiene: I found two plates that still have stains from the pervious owner. And that’s suppose to be washed with a dish washing machine. The tap water on the table tasted like fish which they actually put their water next to where they clean the dishes.  

Food: was not a wow to me and is not anything special that draws my attention compare to JW Marriott. 

Overall. Floors dirty. Water taste like fish. Hygiene is low and staff is poorly trained.

Farm House is a good clean place with a good sea view to enjoy a lunch buffet  in the new hotel in North Point ---Vic. Farm House is a new restaurant of the hotel. Food is quite good  with varieties. Customers will be satisfied especially with promotion price now.

A newly opened restaurant located within Hotel Vic serving western and Chinese cuisines on both buffet and a la carte basis. The seating and overall environment is nice with a harbour view. Standard of food is also nice and the writer would recommend Club Sandwich. However, the pricing is much on the high when a regular coffee without refill costs HK$68 per cup!
Good presentation and the fresh grilled US sirloin beef was very good

Lots of seating inside in different configurations with a couple of private rooms. 

Went for lunch buffet during a weekday and the selection was limited but just right. Regular refresh of popular items namely sashimi and a good variation of choices.

reviews.text:
💐 母親節前一天，見仍有位，算係新酒店，又係新鴻基集團，午市自助餐平日信用卡有折，今次母親節前夕沒有加價，但不可享信用卡或其他優惠，成人每位 HKD398，小童 (11歲或以下)及長者有半價優惠，這些條件，即刻訂位一試😊。
🏨 海匯酒店地理位置鄰近北角碼頭、港鐵站、即使乘搭巴士、電車等交通工具亦不算很遠，交通算便利，座落地點與北角主要街道之繁忙相比，都算是保留一點靜中帶旺的感覺。
🍽 自助餐食物：
🥗 冷盤有一般的 Cold Cut、Parma Ham、沙律，但就真的很一般，連平日可自由添加的果仁、果乾及脆煙肉粒等材料都無。
🍣 魚生有４款，壽司連我平日喜愛的蛋壽司及油揚都無，更不用說 Soba 了。
🍲 熱盤有燒羊架、澳洲西冷、熟蠔、沙爹雞串燒、粉麵檔、即炒意粉（材料係茄醬、蘑菇、洋蔥）、點心有蝦餃、粉果、花卷、馬拉糕、雞粥、燒鴨、叉燒、燒肉、雞翼、牛仔骨、炸三文魚頭腩等
🦐 海鮮有蝦、青口及蜆
🍰 甜品最特色係將 Waffles 做成長葉形🌿，但每次一機只能做４枝，每次要等10多20分鐘，真是少一點耐性都很難食到，幸好當日未有 Full House，見到食客們都很有質素，很禮貌禮讓，亦體諒工作人員。
但 Waffles 與 Pancake 的餡料只有罐頭生果，連新鮮士多啤梨🍓及藍莓都欠奉，唯有問工作人員要一杯牛奶公司雪糕吧🍨。
係呀！雪糕係等工作人員代取，不是自助的。
📝 總結今次自助餐性價比不高，如果是長者半價還可以。 幸好冷盤及甜品放在精美的凍櫃內，感覺衛生美觀，加上裝修優雅舒適，把評分推高一點。

服務態度     👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻
環境            👍🏻👍🏻
食物質素     👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻
物超所值     👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻
備註: 早餐buffet太豐富，有鮮榨果汁、粥很綿、炒麵不咸、環境普通、光線充足、靠窗望東區走廊橋底、收餐具速度很有效率。

下午茶垃圾，所謂嘅日本綠茶主題，但得個樣，咸點口味組合奇怪(燒鰻魚下面加塊好似擺咗好耐嘅隔夜麵包、鴨肝外包住綠茶啫哩)。甜點尤其恐佈，全部(綠茶卷蛋，銅鑼燒餅等)非常之乾。水信玄餅嘅質地好奇怪。
散叫正常，薯條正常、燒鱈魚可取(雖然伴碟嘅zucchini 好苦)，但就因為服務差完全被扣分。全場只有十枱客左右，職員甚多，但叫人無人理，所有正常要求(加水、落單)要重複多次，向不同職員催促，催咗幾次仍然有漏。

以食物種類來計，lunch buffet是超貴，不值。只是環境好，服務好。
詳細點評:
1) 座位有部份是海景位，就算不是，因新裝修，環境不俗。
2) 服務質素一如普通酒店，態度好。
3)只得一個冷盤區，和熱盤區。冷盤區只有青口，蝦，三文魚刺身，吞拿魚刺身，沙律，電糕只有牛奶公司。熱盤區有牛扒，粥，面，包，點心，咖哩薄餅。
4)特點有懷舊樽裝汽水。
5) 粥唔夠熱
6)牛扒過熟
總結:
228蚊連加一，只食以上食物絕對不抵食，只是環境好而已。

Overall. Floors dirty. Water taste like fish. Hygiene is low and staff is poorly trained.

reviews.text:
New Hotel in North Point Hong Kong=- Nice View of Harbour, and having been to Hong Kong around 30 times- I would probably have given three and a half stars. Hotel has rather odd layout.. a nice fountain, and then when you go into hotel most of ground floor is taken up by shops  selling fragrances- with no one in except the sales staff.. the registration is on the second floor. Definitely not 5 star standards re staff training.. had to use computer to find direction to most famous landmarks, shuttle to central for the airport train... but surely it is not beyond the wit of man to train  staff to smile...or say have a nice day?
No central area near reception to chat with other holiday makers..
Would I go back? Actually not in this case.

Been here several times now and it's a great hotel. Most of the staff are friendly and helpful but one or two are definitely not happy to be working there. The breakfast buffet is great with loads of options. The rooms are really great and if you get a harbour view, you'll see some fantastic sunsets. Cleaning staff are so polite and couldn't be more helpful too.

Chic hotel in North Point which has a number of great restaurants attached, with a bar as well. The view from the harbour-facing rooms is great, and rooms come at an affordable price as well. The bottom flies also have a shopping mall attached. This hotel is overall a new, fairly unknown one and the value here is amazing.

Brand new hotel with good sized rooms with modern fittings plus power shower. Good service team. Love the rooftop bar. Easy access to MTR rocks (5min walk) plus there’s a fruit store and Watson’s nearby to sort out any of your needs. Definitely coming back next in Hong Kong.

Very good services and rooms are clean. Bay view is gorgeous. Hotel have settled goes to near by town centers for shopping and dinning.  Subway access is just hundred yards away.  Other public transportation s are close by.   I like this hotel and it's location.

非常推薦！離北角站蠻近的 （A1出口）
雖然房間不算大，但非常舒適且非常整潔
有很多貼心的準備
飯店有24小時健身房、無邊界泳池可以使用
入住第一天房間有提供免費的mini bar，還有膠囊咖啡機可以使用！
吹風機是大台的，對長頭髮的女生來說非常貼心
房間提供免費手機可以連上網使用，也可以免費撥打特定國家國際電話和香港本地，非常便利！！
（若開起網路共享才需要額外費用）
房間都有海景，主要是窗戶的大小、規格不同
23樓有露天酒吧可以在晚上放鬆看夜景
如果不想被送錯東西到房間,跟你說馬上來取走,但你等了半小時都不來,趁你不在才默默進房取走,不想要光是辦個入住就要等很久等到前面的人都喊要投訴了飯店還是無感,不想要要拿杯子使用卻發現遺留上一個房客的咖啡以及湯匙上有一圈乾掉的咖啡垢,不想要房間沒有清理,請不要選擇它,同樣的價位會有更好的選擇!
